# Logging

Use `logEvent` / `logger` from shared logger — **not** `console.log`. Full detail: `apps/index-pdf-backend/LOGGING.md`.

- `event`: `domain.action`; include `requestId` (and `userId` when relevant).
- Structured `metadata`, not string interpolation.
- No secrets, tokens, full PDFs, or huge prompts (logger redacts common fields).
